lead_paragraph: Rookie Gary Sanchez keeps putting up numbers at an astounding rate — and putting the New York Yankees in position to make a run at a playoff spot.

headline.print_headline: Sanchez Hits 2 More Homers, Yankees Beat Rays 11-5
